<subSubSection pageId="164" pageNumber="165" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="164.[151,1437,1518,1905]" pageId="164" pageNumber="165">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[268,491,1735,1761]" pageId="164" pageNumber="165" refId="ref369190" refString="Rondani, C. (1863) Diptera exotica revisa et annotata novis nonnullis descriptis. Eredi Soliani, Modena, 99 pp., 1 pl. [This is the separate that came out before the journal version with a different title, here as Rondani (1864 a)]." type="book" year="1863">Rondani (1863: 73)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<emphasis box="[616,884,1735,1761]" italics="true" pageId="164" pageNumber="165">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1863" box="[616,880,1735,1761]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Cyrthosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="164" pageNumber="165" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="meridionalis">Cyrthosia meridionalis</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
without specifying either the 
<taxonomicName box="[1229,1315,1735,1761]" family="Number" pageId="164" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
or the sex of the specimens, but giving a single measurement of length, from material received from E. Truqui and A. Schembri. This nominal species was described under the generic name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1863" box="[1031,1141,1807,1833]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Cyrthosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="164" pageNumber="165" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1031,1141,1807,1833]" italics="true" pageId="164" pageNumber="165">Cyrthosia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which is an “unjustified emendation of 
<taxonomicName authority="Perris, 1839" authorityName="Perris" authorityYear="1839" box="[367,608,1843,1869]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Cyrtosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="164" pageNumber="165" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[367,463,1843,1869]" italics="true" pageId="164" pageNumber="165">Cyrtosia</emphasis>
Perris, 1839
</taxonomicName>
” (
<bibRefCitation author="O'Hara, J. E. &amp; Cerretti, P. &amp; Pape, T. &amp; Evenhuis, N. L." box="[633,891,1843,1870]" pageId="164" pageNumber="165" pagination="1 - 268" refId="ref361577" refString="O'Hara, J. E., Cerretti, P., Pape, T. &amp; Evenhuis, N. L. (2011) Nomenclatural studies toward a world list of Diptera genus-group names. Part II: Camillo Rondani. Zootaxa, 3141, 1 - 268. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3141.1.1" type="journal article" year="2011">
O’Hara 
<emphasis box="[726,782,1843,1869]" italics="true" pageId="164" pageNumber="165">et al.</emphasis>
2011: 69
</bibRefCitation>
). We could not locate any 
<typeStatus box="[1186,1234,1843,1869]" pageId="164" pageNumber="165">type</typeStatus>
specimens of this nominal species during our study.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
